Package: second-hand
Architecture: any
Pre-Depends: dpkg (>= 1.16.1)
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, python3, chrony
Provides: chrony-dashboard
Description: Chrony time statistics dashboard
 A web dashboard for monitoring chrony NTP synchronization status.
 Displays tracking info, time sources, and synchronization statistics.
 .
 Features:
  * Real-time tracking status and synchronization state
  * Time source overview with reachability indicators
  * Source statistics including offset, jitter, and skew
  * RTC (real-time clock) monitoring when available
 .
 Includes all Python dependencies in a self-contained virtualenv.
 Runs as a systemd service on port 8000 by default.
